babe is trying to talk Mr. Takamori
into something!

Mayor Takamori. Thank you very
much for inviting me in as a special
exchange student and goodwill

My people would like nothing more

friendship with the people of
Shibuya. Now, let us join hands

72:
Alk, Stella! Just what in the world are
you wearing?!
77:
I was about to ask you the same
thing.
82:
You infiltrated the school to... take
down Palpebra?

That is correct! I am playing the role
of a special exchange student and
goodwill ambassador as cover. In
due time, Shibuya and Mirea will be
allies!

I burned with envy every time I laid
eyes on your adorable uniforms... So
I had this outfit custom-made for
me!
95:

and strong.

Nothing about that outfit screams

Do you think that maybe you don't

154:
Oh? Are you suuure? Even after
going to the trouble of getting such
a cute outfit made? I know how
much you're looking forward to the
festival...
158:
I just want to know how you really
feel, Toria!
167:
Cut it out, Nao. You can't just ask
people questions like that!
171:
Heh-heh. That's how you do things,
Ayumu. I've got my own way
180:
The reason I've been having such
fun is because I've grown fond of
Palpebra?!
189:
It can't be... The people of Mirea

193:
As princess, I MUST share their
feelings for the accursed Palpebra!
198:
Huh. Okay, I think I see what's going
on here.
202:
Hey, Toria. Love and hate?
Sometimes it's not so easy to tell the
difference between them.
205:
You hate Palpebra so much that you
love it, right? I understand that
feeling... So...
209:
Let me help you stomp Palpebra
into the dust!
217:
Of course I am! I even know of a
super powerful, totally ruthless way
to bring Palpebra down. So let me
help you!
222:
Hold it, Nao. What do you think
you're
226:

To land a good hit on your

be ruthless. For example...
237:
Sometimes you've gotta draw all
over the chalkboard! Don't stop until

241:
My! I knew you were a pirate, but
you're even more ruthless than I

246:
Heh... I'm just getting started. Wait

258:
I shall!

272:
Once we arrive at the cafeteria, I will

275:
I wanted to try "treating you" at least

279:
Yes, my princess! It would be an

283:
Haha.

Hehe! That's 'cause I'm having a lot

295:
Yeah, but that's because she's just

301:
Relax, man. Your sister knows what

305:
I am moved by your enthusiastic

308:
Truly, the Legendary Four of Mirea

Yay! That makes me super happy!

317:

all!
